# Design Doc Routing

Design docs are modular under `docs/design/`. Start with `docs/design/README.md` to pick only the docs you need.

Do NOT auto-load `docs/design/core-architecture.md` for runtime-local or test-local work.

Load `docs/design/core-architecture.md` only for new features, cross-domain changes, save/events/persistence changes, or when local intent is unclear.

**Coding standards:** `.agent/skills/unity-project-conventions/SKILL.md`
